stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: Client HTTP Ingestion (XADD)
    Pending --> Processing: Worker Read (XREADGROUP)
    
    state Processing {
        [*] --> CheckIdempotency: SET idempotency:key NX
        CheckIdempotency --> CheckStep: StateManager.get_last_step()
        CheckStep --> ExecuteStep: Run Handler Business Logic
        ExecuteStep --> SaveStep: StateManager.save_step()
    }

    Processing --> Completed: All Steps Finish
    Processing --> DelayedRetry: Transient Failure (attempt < 5)
    Processing --> DLQ: NonRetryableError OR attempt >= 5

    DelayedRetry --> Pending: ZSET Timeout Expired -> Re-enqueue XADD
    DLQ --> Pending: Operator POST /dlq/{service}/{id}/replay
    Completed --> [*]: XACK & XDEL
